147
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:36,820
I see him every day.

148
00:08:37,460 --> 00:08:39,030
Are you sure you're not mistaken?

149
00:08:41,670 --> 00:08:42,980
Your ID is missing,

150
00:08:43,550 --> 00:08:44,670
and you can't explain why.

151
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:46,980
So many people died

152
