165
00:09:08,820 --> 00:09:10,910
But how did your ID end up with him?

166
00:09:11,580 --> 00:09:14,190
He got it from me.

167
00:09:14,430 --> 00:09:15,550
This is a serious situation.

168
00:09:15,550 --> 00:09:16,940
Just tell the truth.

169
00:09:16,940 --> 00:09:18,980
Do you really think
you can fool the police?

170
00:09:18,980 --> 00:09:20,820
You haven't even had a wife yet.

171
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:22,630
All right. All right!

172
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:25,820
About two months ago,

173
00:09:25,820 --> 00:09:26,700
Jiang Peng came to me.

174
00:09:26,700 --> 00:09:28,910
He asked to borrow my ID for a bit.

175
00:09:29,190 --> 00:09:29,980
Lin, one more drink.

176
00:09:36,430 --> 00:09:38,060
Lin, I came to have a drink with you

177
00:09:38,060 --> 00:09:39,060
because I need a favor.

178
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:42,940
Can I borrow your ID for a while?

179
00:09:42,940 --> 00:09:44,860
I want to go to the internet café
to play games.

180
00:09:45,820 --> 00:09:47,190
You finally feel like playing?

181
00:09:48,100 --> 00:09:49,430
That's the spirit!

182
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,940
(Name: Wu Shenglin)
Go and have fun.

183
00:09:52,910 --> 00:09:54,100
Where's your ID?

184
00:09:54,390 --> 00:09:55,270
Why do you need mine?

185
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:56,740
They kept mine as collateral.

186
00:09:56,740 --> 00:09:57,830
They haven't given it back.

187
00:09:58,060 --> 00:09:58,940
Those scums.

188
00:10:00,740 --> 00:10:01,630
Tomorrow, I'll go

189
00:10:02,100 --> 00:10:03,150
and curse them out for you.

190
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:03,940
Take it.

191
00:10:05,190 --> 00:10:05,860
Thanks, Lin.

192
00:10:11,270 --> 00:10:12,190
