193
00:10:13,980 --> 00:10:14,910
Just let it go.

194
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:16,630
If you can let it go,

195
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:17,790
all will be good.

196
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:23,100
Two days later, he told me

197
00:10:23,100 --> 00:10:26,190
