199
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:28,790
I figured

200
00:10:28,790 --> 00:10:30,460
he didn't do it on purpose.

201
00:10:30,860 --> 00:10:31,630
Besides,

202
00:10:31,630 --> 00:10:33,460
getting a new ID isn't that troublesome.

203
00:10:33,460 --> 00:10:34,700
So I didn't say anything.

204
00:10:35,740 --> 00:10:37,630
You just casually lent out

205
