206
00:10:39,100 --> 00:10:40,550
Jiang Peng was a good guy.

207
00:10:40,550 --> 00:10:41,940
He often buys me drinks.

208
00:10:41,940 --> 00:10:43,630
When my family was struggling,

209
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:44,790
