212
00:10:47,980 --> 00:10:49,150
Mr. Wang, isn't that right?

213
00:10:49,150 --> 00:10:50,700
Right?

214
00:10:50,700 --> 00:10:51,630
What's right about that?

215
00:10:51,630 --> 00:10:54,060
Do you want to spend a few days
behind bars?

216
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:55,550
I've watched you grow up.

217
00:10:55,550 --> 00:10:57,250
I know exactly
what kind of person you are.

218
00:10:57,430 --> 00:10:59,460
You must've gotten something in return.

219
00:10:59,740 --> 00:11:01,820
