223
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:07,060
I'll say it. I asked him for 500 yuan.

224
00:11:07,340 --> 00:11:09,150
First, he gave me 200 yuan
as collateral.

225
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:10,700
Then he paid me another 300 yuan.

226
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:12,910
That's not illegal, is it?

227
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:14,100
All this trouble

228
00:11:14,100 --> 00:11:15,580
for 500 yuan?

229
00:11:15,580 --> 00:11:16,100
Enough!

230
00:11:21,670 --> 00:11:22,460
I want both of you

231
