233
00:11:26,700 --> 00:11:27,500
You, come over here.

234
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,670
You, face the other way.

235
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:39,270
This one.

236
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:40,510
Are you sure?

237
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:41,220
Yes, I'm sure.

238
00:11:41,430 --> 00:11:42,030
Okay.

