248
00:12:22,940 --> 00:12:23,700
No.

249
00:12:23,940 --> 00:12:26,510
He came to our village over a year ago.

250
00:12:27,100 --> 00:12:28,630
He's from Xinquan.

251
00:12:28,910 --> 00:12:30,860
He had no family
and wanted to make a living.

252
00:12:31,390 --> 00:12:32,790
So he worked at the quarry.

253
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:34,100
He was honest and hardworking.

254
00:12:34,110 --> 00:12:36,060
Someone in the village
even took a liking to him

255
00:12:36,060 --> 00:12:37,220
and was making him

256
00:12:37,220 --> 00:12:38,550
